Summary of Changes

The changes wrap each resource name in an <a> tag with:

· href attribute pointing to the official website URL
· target="_blank" to open links in a new tab
· rel="noopener noreferrer" for security when opening external links
· style="color: var(--primary-dark); text-decoration: none;" to maintain the existing visual style (dark green text, no underline)
· The <strong> tag is moved inside the link so the resource name remains bold

